60f29f05-7be7-4194-a406-05ce474d74af.title: 'Black-eye'
60f29f05-7be7-4194-a406-05ce474d74af.text: Ah, we be building this 'ere tower. Lookin' good ain't it?

f20182d1-8b2e-49b2-bb33-10f789c4e9dc.title: <player>
f20182d1-8b2e-49b2-bb33-10f789c4e9dc.text:
It does look pretty impressive, but what are you doing
hanging around?

d8b5f4d1-320c-4094-a78b-f61964dbd69d.title: <player>
d8b5f4d1-320c-4094-a78b-f61964dbd69d.text: Naturally. Not sure why I asked.

916c47f3-4818-4671-ba90-ac50c18699fc.title: 'Black-eye'
916c47f3-4818-4671-ba90-ac50c18699fc.text: You'll find a kettle in the box to the-

a3f658b8-cc10-4705-b438-610a78c3e5e4.title: <player>
a3f658b8-cc10-4705-b438-610a78c3e5e4.text:
I was just wondering if you might be able to help me
out with one?

b73aafea-2f25-40ad-b4ab-1da2e35468bd.title: 'Black-eye'
b73aafea-2f25-40ad-b4ab-1da2e35468bd.text:
Always glad to help a budding builder. But first, prove
your Construction knowledge by answering some
questions.

5ace06e8-4144-4446-a839-1f8edfdfe5ea.title: 'Black-eye'
5ace06e8-4144-4446-a839-1f8edfdfe5ea.text: How many nails does it take to make a rocking chair?

84b5011c-4771-4ced-8abb-7a50bb03d901.title: 'Black-eye'
84b5011c-4771-4ced-8abb-7a50bb03d901.text: One? How do you suppose you'd use a single nail?

23ebef87-0b83-4e4b-b412-80c6225f0cd5.title: 'Black-eye'
23ebef87-0b83-4e4b-b412-80c6225f0cd5.text:
Bingo! Okay, now what takes 3 planks, 3 cloths and 3
nails to make, and helps remove light from a room?

92fb4f4c-0560-4998-9e1e-4466e351de31.title: 'Black-eye'
92fb4f4c-0560-4998-9e1e-4466e351de31.text:
Of course, because that's what everyone needs - a rug
up at their window.

ecc8b96d-e91e-498d-96ff-0d223420f5eb.title: 'Black-eye'
ecc8b96d-e91e-498d-96ff-0d223420f5eb.text:
Those curtains are not going to be in any way opulent,
matey.

012e9fad-7eec-430f-bfda-c064a4bbeade.title: 'Black-eye'
012e9fad-7eec-430f-bfda-c064a4bbeade.text:
Nice one. Last question: I like fish and I want to put
some in my garden, but I need a special water feature.
What materials would I require?

1ebffe98-f831-41f2-86dc-1534a7beb760.title: 'Black-eye'
1ebffe98-f831-41f2-86dc-1534a7beb760.text: Oh, and you were so close!

65d5d6a7-8a38-40a0-8c4a-c5e925ab6965.title: 'Black-eye'
65d5d6a7-8a38-40a0-8c4a-c5e925ab6965.text:
That's it! You seem to know your stuff. I got a spare
helmet from a builder that died on... I mean, err, had
to leave the job for greener pastures.

a8b4a07f-0b3b-478d-a695-bbc44ff950e7.title: <player>
a8b4a07f-0b3b-478d-a695-bbc44ff950e7.text: Wait a minute! Is there blood on this helmet?

258f9af0-d31c-41e9-8b51-3019014f56b4.title: 'Black-eye'
258f9af0-d31c-41e9-8b51-3019014f56b4.text:
Erm, no, that's just, erm, paint. Yes, paint! That's what
it is!

ff5acc40-b303-490c-b57e-df850fe29d17.title: 'Black-eye'
ff5acc40-b303-490c-b57e-df850fe29d17.text: Yes - just as nice as the one you're carrying I'd say.

99ac8fab-67d6-4d8b-81cf-67587ac58101.title: <player>
99ac8fab-67d6-4d8b-81cf-67587ac58101.text: I've got one just like it stored somewhere.

66f2bde7-0e0c-4400-b68b-c3df0ecc4ca0.title: 'Black-eye'
66f2bde7-0e0c-4400-b68b-c3df0ecc4ca0.text: Well I am so very pleased!

71a72f5d-ac65-4145-ba6a-cdc52d995456.title: 'Black-eye'
71a72f5d-ac65-4145-ba6a-cdc52d995456.text:
Why, thanks. Some would say as nice as the one you're
wearing!
